; Coverage test for draft.cc lines 458-459: negative cost error
; When a draft template posting has a negative cost value,
; the code throws a parse_error. Exercises:
;   L458: if (post.cost->sign() < 0) -- true branch
;   L459: throw parse_error("A posting's cost may not be negative")

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    10 AAPL @ $5.00
    Assets:Cash   $-50.00

test xact 2024/06/15 Grocery to Expenses:Food '@' '$-6.00' '10 AAPL' from Assets:Cash -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: A posting's cost may not be negative
end test
